title: Filiz Kocaman
summary: Filiz Kocaman (born February 23, 1985 in Tokat) is a Turkish volleyball player. She is 178 cm and plays as libero. She plays for Fenerbahçe Women's Volleyball Team since 2007 season start and wear 14 number. She played 43 times for national team. She also played for Eczacıbaşı, Şişli, Yalovaspor and Konya Selçuk University.
